title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Aug 30 2021

description:
Befuddled Sec of State Blinken wants us to trust the Taliban. The Biden White House is going to wait out the news cycle and act like the Afghanistan disaster never happened. Lt. Col. Stuart Scheller calls for accountability, is relieved of his command. Will there be accountability for epic Afghanistan failure? DeSantis vs. Fauci. Twitter permanently suspends Alex Berenson over coronavirus tweets.
